        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK285">
<l>aruḷkaruti yaṉpuṭaiya rātal poruḷkarutip</l>
<l>poccāppup pārppārka ṇil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The study of kindness and the exercise of benevolence is not with those who watch for another's forgetfulness, though desire of his property.</l>
